name: CONCRETE JUNGLE - NAIL APPLIQUE
description:
THIS IS A LIMITED EDITION NAIL PHUNK EXCLUSIVE
LIMITED TO 1500pcs
ONCE THEY ARE GONE, THEY'RE GONE!!!

NAIL PHUNK APPLIQUES
- CONTENTS
*  20 NAIL STRIP APPLIQUES (FITS ALL NAIL SIZES)
*  NAIL FILE
*  CUTICLE WAND
*  PACKAGE RE-SEALER (FOR FUTURE USE)
- LASTS UP TO 10 DAYS
- NO DRY TIME
- NO SMUDGING 
- EASY PEEL APPLY TECHNOLOGY
- REMOVE WITH NAIL POLISH REMOVER 

INSTRUCTIONS
1.) pull off clear strip
2.) hold silver tab and peel away appropriate applique
3.) choose nail applique
4.) apply, stretch and press firmly on nail
5.) take wooden cuticle wand and shape to nail, firmly pressing around edges with one end
6.) fold excess applique against the edge of your nail to easily tear away excess
7.) file in a downward motion to smooth edges
